<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <link href ='review.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' />
</head>
<body>
    <div id="review_header">
        <h1>Please let us know what you think about our service!</h1>
    </div>
    <div id='endScreen' style='display:none;'>
        <br>
        <b>Thank you for your feedback. We really appreciate the time you took to help us improve our service.</b>
        <br><br>
        <b>Also, see what others have to say about us <u id='toRevPage' class='toRevPage'>here</u>!</b>
    </div>
    <div id="review_info">
        <div id = "rateUs">
            <br>
            <div id ='rateP'>
                <b>On a scale of 1 to 5, what would you rate us?</b>
            </div>
            <div class = 'radBut'>
                <input type ='radio' name ='scale'/>
                <br>
                Awful
            </div>
            <div class = 'radBut'>
                <input type ='radio' name ='scale'/>
                <br>
                Bad
            </div>
            <div class = 'radBut'>
                <input type ='radio' name ='scale'/>
                <br>
                Okay
            </div>
            <div class = 'radBut'>
                <input type ='radio' name ='scale'/>
                <br>
                Good
            </div>
            <div class = 'radBut'>
                <input type ='radio' name ='scale'/>
                <br>
                Excellent
            </div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <br>
            <div>
                <b>What do you think about our service?</b>
            </div>
            <br>
            <textarea rows='6' cols='97' placeholder='Leave your feedback here...'></textarea>
        </div>
        <div>
            <br>
            <div>
            <b>How would you suggest us improve it?</b>
            </div>
            <br>
            <textarea rows='6' cols='97' placeholder='Leave your feedback here...'></textarea>
        </div>
            <br>
            <button id='reviewSub'>Submit</button>
            <button id='toRevBut' class='toRevPage'>See others' comments</button>
    </div>
    <div id='revPage' style='display:none;'>
        <div id ='revPageHeader'>
            <p id ='backBut'><i id="backArrow"></i> <u>Go back</u></p>
            <h1>Comments</h1>
        </div>
        <div id ='cmtDisplay'>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src='review.js'></script>
</body>
</html>